---
---

<section class="faq-section bg-cream">
	<div class="faq-inner">
		<header class="faq-header">
			<p class="font-body text-[0.68rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[2.8px] text-gold-dark/80 sm:text-[0.72rem]">
				Bengal Excellence
			</p>
			<h2 class="mt-3 font-heading text-[2.2rem] font-medium tracking-tight text-dark sm:text-[2.8rem] lg:text-[3.3rem]">
				Frequently Asked Questions
			</h2>
			<span class="mx-auto mt-4 block h-px w-24 bg-(--gold-line) sm:w-28"></span>
			<p class="section-subtitle">Everything you need to know about our Bengal kittens and adoption process</p>
		</header>

		<div class="faq-container">

			<div class="faq-item">
				<input type="checkbox" id="faq1" class="faq-toggle" />
				<label for="faq1" class="faq-question" tabindex="0">
					<span>How much does a Bengal kitten cost?</span>
					<span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				</label>
				<div class="faq-content">
					<div class="faq-content-inner">
						<p>Pricing varies based on lineage, markings, and availability. Our Bengal kittens typically range from premium to show-quality pricing.</p>
						<div class="price-highlight">
							<p><strong>Price Range:</strong> Contact us for current pricing and available kittens. Each kitten is individually assessed for quality, temperament, and show potential.</p>
						</div>
						<p>Please contact us for a personalized quote and detailed information about our current litters.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-item">
				<input type="checkbox" id="faq2" class="faq-toggle" />
				<label for="faq2" class="faq-question" tabindex="0">
					<span>Are your kittens health tested?</span>
					<span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				</label>
				<div class="faq-content">
					<div class="faq-content-inner">
						<p>Yes, all our kittens undergo comprehensive health testing to ensure they are healthy and genetically sound.</p>
						<p><strong>Our testing includes:</strong></p>
						<ul>
							<li>HCM (Hypertrophic Cardiomyopathy) screening</li>
							<li>PK-Def (Pyruvate Kinase Deficiency) testing</li>
							<li>Complete veterinary health examination</li>
							<li>Age-appropriate vaccinations</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="trust-badge">Written Health Guarantee Included</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-item">
				<input type="checkbox" id="faq3" class="faq-toggle" />
				<label for="faq3" class="faq-question" tabindex="0">
					<span>What is the adoption process?</span>
					<span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				</label>
				<div class="faq-content">
					<div class="faq-content-inner">
						<p>Our adoption process is designed to ensure the perfect match between kitten and family.</p>
						<p><strong>The process includes:</strong></p>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>Initial Consultation:</strong> We discuss your lifestyle and preferences</li>
							<li><strong>Application:</strong> Complete our adoption application form</li>
							<li><strong>Approval &amp; Contract:</strong> Review and sign our adoption agreement</li>
							<li><strong>Deposit:</strong> Secure your chosen kitten with a deposit</li>
							<li><strong>Updates:</strong> Receive regular photos and videos until pickup</li>
						</ul>
						<p>Visit our contact page for more details about each step of the process.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-item">
				<input type="checkbox" id="faq4" class="faq-toggle" />
				<label for="faq4" class="faq-question" tabindex="0">
					<span>Do you offer shipping and delivery?</span>
					<span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				</label>
				<div class="faq-content">
					<div class="faq-content-inner">
						<p>Yes, we provide safe and comfortable shipping options for families who cannot pick up in person.</p>
						<p><strong>Delivery options:</strong></p>
						<ul>
							<li>Ground transportation within the UK</li>
							<li>Flight nanny service for international delivery</li>
							<li>Climate-controlled pet courier services</li>
							<li>Personal pickup at our location (preferred)</li>
						</ul>
						<p>All transportation is handled with the utmost care for your kitten's wellbeing. Contact us to discuss logistics, timing, and associated costs.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-item">
				<input type="checkbox" id="faq5" class="faq-toggle" />
				<label for="faq5" class="faq-question" tabindex="0">
					<span>What care do Bengal cats require?</span>
					<span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				</label>
				<div class="faq-content">
					<div class="faq-content-inner">
						<p>Bengals are active, intelligent cats that thrive with proper care and enrichment.</p>
						<p><strong>Essential care requirements:</strong></p>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>Diet:</strong> High-quality, protein-rich cat food</li>
							<li><strong>Grooming:</strong> Weekly brushing to maintain coat health</li>
							<li><strong>Exercise:</strong> Interactive play sessions daily</li>
							<li><strong>Enrichment:</strong> Climbing structures, puzzle toys, and mental stimulation</li>
							<li><strong>Veterinary:</strong> Annual check-ups and preventive care</li>
						</ul>
						<p>We provide a comprehensive care guide with each kitten to ensure a smooth transition to your home.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-item">
				<input type="checkbox" id="faq6" class="faq-toggle" />
				<label for="faq6" class="faq-question" tabindex="0">
					<span>What makes your Bengal cattery different?</span>
					<span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				</label>
				<div class="faq-content">
					<div class="faq-content-inner">
						<p>We are committed to breeding exceptional Bengals with outstanding temperament and health.</p>
						<p><strong>Our breeding philosophy:</strong></p>
						<ul>
							<li>Focus on temperament, health, and breed standard</li>
							<li>Kittens raised in our home with early socialization</li>
							<li>Premium nutrition and veterinary care</li>
							<li>Individual attention to ensure confident, well-adjusted kittens</li>
							<li>Ongoing support for the life of your Bengal</li>
						</ul>
						<p>Each kitten is treated as a member of our family until they join yours.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-item">
				<input type="checkbox" id="faq7" class="faq-toggle" />
				<label for="faq7" class="faq-question" tabindex="0">
					<span>Can I visit your cattery before adopting?</span>
					<span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				</label>
				<div class="faq-content">
					<div class="faq-content-inner">
						<p>We welcome approved applicants to visit and meet our cats and kittens by appointment.</p>
						<p><strong>Visit guidelines:</strong></p>
						<ul>
							<li>Visits are scheduled after application approval</li>
							<li>Biosecurity protocols are in place to protect our cats</li>
							<li>Meet our breeding cats and available kittens</li>
							<li>See our home environment and care practices</li>
							<li>Ask questions and get to know us personally</li>
						</ul>
						<p>This gives you the opportunity to see our breeding practices firsthand and ensure we're the right fit for your family.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-item">
				<input type="checkbox" id="faq8" class="faq-toggle" />
				<label for="faq8" class="faq-question" tabindex="0">
					<span>What age do kittens go to their new homes?</span>
					<span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				</label>
				<div class="faq-content">
					<div class="faq-content-inner">
						<p>Our kittens are ready for adoption at 12–14 weeks of age, ensuring they are fully prepared for their new homes.</p>
						<p><strong>Why we wait until 12–14 weeks:</strong></p>
						<ul>
							<li>Complete vaccination series</li>
							<li>Proper socialization with mother and littermates</li>
							<li>Development of essential behavioral skills</li>
							<li>Weaned and eating independently</li>
							<li>Litter box training fully established</li>
						</ul>
						<p>This extended time ensures your kitten has the best foundation for a healthy, confident life with you.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-item">
				<input type="checkbox" id="faq9" class="faq-toggle" />
				<label for="faq9" class="faq-question" tabindex="0">
					<span>Do you offer breeding rights?</span>
					<span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				</label>
				<div class="faq-content">
					<div class="faq-content-inner">
						<p>Breeding rights are available on select kittens to qualified, experienced breeders only.</p>
						<p><strong>Requirements for breeding rights:</strong></p>
						<ul>
							<li>Demonstrated experience in ethical breeding practices</li>
							<li>Commitment to health testing and breed standards</li>
							<li>Appropriate breeding facilities and environment</li>
							<li>References from veterinarians and other breeders</li>
							<li>Additional contract terms and pricing apply</li>
						</ul>
						<p>Please discuss your breeding program goals during the consultation process.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-item">
				<input type="checkbox" id="faq10" class="faq-toggle" />
				<label for="faq10" class="faq-question" tabindex="0">
					<span>What support do you provide after adoption?</span>
					<span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				</label>
				<div class="faq-content">
					<div class="faq-content-inner">
						<p>We remain available for guidance and support throughout your Bengal's lifetime.</p>
						<p><strong>Ongoing support includes:</strong></p>
						<ul>
							<li>24/7 availability for urgent questions or concerns</li>
							<li>Dietary and nutrition guidance</li>
							<li>Behavioral consultation and training tips</li>
							<li>Health and wellness advice</li>
							<li>Community of Bengal owners for peer support</li>
						</ul>
						<p>We love receiving updates about our kittens as they grow and thrive in their forever homes!</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

		<div class="faq-cta">
			<h3 class="faq-cta-heading">Get in touch with us today.</h3>
			<a href="https://luxuryrosettes.co.uk/contact/" class="faq-cta-btn">
				<span>Contact Us Today</span>
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.faq-section {
		width: 100%;
	}

	.faq-inner {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 5rem 2rem 6rem;
	}

	.faq-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
	}

	.section-subtitle {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.5vw, 1.05rem);
		font-weight: 400;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5a5a5a);
		max-width: 620px;
		margin: 1.25rem auto 0;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.faq-container {
		max-width: 860px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.faq-item {
		background: #fff;
		border-radius: 12px;
		margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
		overflow: hidden;
		border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
		transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.faq-item:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.13);
	}

	.faq-toggle {
		position: absolute;
		opacity: 0;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.faq-question {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		padding: 1.4rem 1.75rem;
		cursor: pointer;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		line-height: 1.4;
		color: var(--dark);
		transition: color 0.25s ease;
		user-select: none;
	}

	.faq-question span:first-child {
		flex: 1;
	}

	.faq-question:hover {
		color: var(--gold-dark);
	}

	.faq-question:focus-visible {
		outline: 3px solid var(--gold);
		outline-offset: -3px;
	}

	/* Icon */
	.faq-icon {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		width: 28px;
		height: 28px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		transition: background 0.3s ease;
		position: relative;
	}

	.faq-icon::before,
	.faq-icon::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		background: var(--gold);
		border-radius: 2px;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.faq-icon::before {
		width: 12px;
		height: 2px;
		top: 50%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
	}

	.faq-icon::after {
		width: 2px;
		height: 12px;
		top: 50%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
	}

	.faq-toggle:checked + .faq-question .faq-icon {
		background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.18);
	}

	.faq-toggle:checked + .faq-question .faq-icon::after {
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(90deg);
	}

	/* Content */
	.faq-content {
		max-height: 0;
		overflow: hidden;
		transition: max-height 0.4s ease;
		padding: 0 1.75rem;
	}

	.faq-content-inner {
		padding: 0 0 1.5rem;
	}

	.faq-toggle:checked + .faq-question + .faq-content {
		max-height: 1200px;
		padding: 0.2rem 1.75rem 0;
	}

	.faq-content p {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: clamp(0.93rem, 1.4vw, 1rem);
		line-height: 1.78;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5a5a5a);
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.faq-content p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.faq-content strong {
		color: var(--dark);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.faq-content ul {
		margin: 0.75rem 0 0.75rem 1.25rem;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.faq-content li {
		margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: clamp(0.91rem, 1.4vw, 0.97rem);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5a5a5a);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	/* Price highlight */
	.price-highlight {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.07), rgba(232, 201, 111, 0.07));
		border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
		padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem;
		margin: 0.9rem 0;
		border-radius: 6px;
	}

	.price-highlight p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--dark);
	}

	/* Trust badge */
	.trust-badge {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.45rem;
		background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.08);
		padding: 0.38rem 0.85rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.83rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #2e7d32;
		margin-top: 0.75rem;
	}

	.trust-badge::before {
		content: '✓';
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 17px;
		height: 17px;
		background: #4caf50;
		color: white;
		border-radius: 50%;
		font-size: 0.68rem;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	/* Responsive */
	@media (max-width: 767px) {
		.faq-inner {
			padding: 3.5rem 1.2rem 4rem;
		}

		.faq-header {
			margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		}

		.faq-question {
			padding: 1.2rem 1.25rem;
			gap: 1rem;
		}

		.faq-content {
			padding: 0 1.25rem;
		}

		.faq-toggle:checked + .faq-question + .faq-content {
			padding: 0.2rem 1.25rem 0;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.faq-inner {
			padding: 2.5rem 1rem 3rem;
		}

		.faq-item {
			margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
			border-radius: 10px;
		}

		.faq-question {
			padding: 1.1rem 1.1rem;
		}
	}

	@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
		.faq-content,
		.faq-item,
		.faq-icon,
		.faq-icon::before,
		.faq-icon::after {
			transition: none !important;
		}
	}

	/* CTA */
	.faq-cta {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 4rem 1rem 1rem;
	}

	.faq-cta-heading {
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
		font-weight: 400;
		color: var(--dark);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.faq-cta-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1rem 2.8rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4af37 0%, #e8c96f 45%, #c59a2f 100%);
		border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4);
		border-radius: 6px;
		color: #fff;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.74rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 3px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		transition: transform 0.5s ease-out, box-shadow 0.5s ease-out;
	}

	.faq-cta-btn::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(115deg, transparent 20%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35) 50%, transparent 80%);
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translateX(-120%);
		transition: transform 0.7s ease, opacity 0.7s ease;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.faq-cta-btn span {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.faq-cta-btn:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-gold-strong);
	}

	.faq-cta-btn:hover::before {
		transform: translateX(120%);
		opacity: 1;
	}
</style>

<script>
	document.querySelectorAll<HTMLInputElement>('.faq-toggle').forEach((checkbox) => {
		checkbox.addEventListener('change', function () {
			if (this.checked) {
				document.querySelectorAll<HTMLInputElement>('.faq-toggle').forEach((other) => {
					if (other !== this) other.checked = false;
				});
			}
		});
	});

	document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.faq-question').forEach((label) => {
		label.addEventListener('keypress', (e) => {
			if (e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') {
				e.preventDefault();
				label.click();
			}
		});
	});
</script>
